<i>noun</i>: 언사 [언사], 발언 [바런] <i>verb</i>: 발언하다 [바런하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>언사 [언사]</dt><br>
<dd>words; remark; language</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 말씨.</dd><br>
<dd>One's words or way of talking.</dd><br>
<dt>발언 [바런]</dt><br>
<dd>comment; remark; statement</dd><br>
<dd>말을 하여 의견을 나타냄. 또는 그 말.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying something to express one's opinion, or a statement made for such a purpose.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>발언하다 [바런하다]</dt><br>
<dd>comment; remark; state</dd><br>
<dd>말을 하여 의견을 나타내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To say something to express one's opinion.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>